posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Capture your sense of style in an apartment home at Walden Pond in Houston near West Oaks Mall.', 'Light-filled interiors match lush green exterior space to create the home you’ve dreamed of and the community you’ve longed for.', 'Walden Pond has it all – the convenience of the city and the modern appeal of suburban living.', 'Discover your best life with an apartment home at Walden Pond.', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'Today', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', 'At Walden Pond, we can’t wait to welcome you and your pets to your new home.', 'Our community is perfectly situated close to parks and recreation for you and your pets.', 'Please review our pet policy details below and contact our friendly leasing team with any additional questions!Maximum of two pets per apartment homeAdditional monthly pet rent may be requiredBreed restrictions: Restricted breeds include but are not limited to Akitas, Chows, Dobermans, German Shepherds, Mastiffs, Pit Bulls, Staffordshire Terrier breeds, Rottweilers, Great Danes, Malamutes, Korean Jindos, Presa Canarios, Huskies, and Wolf Hybrids.', 'Any mixes of these breeds are also prohibited.', 'No exotic pets allowed.', 'Deposit:', 'None', 'Leasing options:', 'Leasing notes:', 'None', 'Application fee:', 'None', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Utilities Cost:', 'None', 'Laundry:', 'Parking type:', 'Parking notes:', 'None', 'Appliances:', 'Exterior:', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Wiring:', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Security and Access:', 'Views:', 'Additional features:', 'Offered by:', 'Walden Pond', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
